    {
      "index": 2,
      "title": "The Foundation: Distributed Ledger Technology",
      "html": "<section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <style>\n    .slide {\n      background-color: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      font-family: var(--font-body);\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;\n      padding: clamp(2rem, 5vh, 5rem);\n      gap: clamp(1rem, 3vh, 3rem);\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n\n    .slide-header h1 {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin: 0;\n      text-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--accent-glow);\n    }\n\n    .slide-content {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n      gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);\n      align-items: start;\n    }\n\n    .concept-text {\n      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n    }\n\n    .concept-text p {\n      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n    }\n\n    .feature-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 1rem;\n    }\n\n    .feature-card {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      padding: 1.5rem;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;\n    }\n\n    .feature-card:hover {\n      border-color: var(--accent);\n      transform: translateX(10px);\n    }\n\n    .feature-card h3 {\n      color: var(--text);\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.4rem);\n      margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;\n    }\n\n    .feature-card p {\n      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.8vw, 1.1rem);\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      animation: fadeInUp 0.6s forwards;\n      animation-delay: var(--delay);\n    }\n\n    @keyframes fadeInUp {\n      to {\n        opacity: 1;\n        transform: translateY(0);\n      }\n    }\n\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n      .slide-content {\n        grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.1s\">The Foundation: Distributed Ledger Technology</h1>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-content\">\n    <div class=\"concept-text reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.3s\">\n      <p>\n        At its core, a <strong>Distributed Ledger</strong> is a database that is consensually shared and synchronized across multiple sites, institutions, or geographies.\n      </p>\n      <p>\n        Unlike traditional databases, there is no central administrator. Every node in the network maintains an identical copy of the ledger, ensuring redundancy and transparency.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n      <div class=\"feature-card reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.5s\">\n        <h3>P2P Networking</h3>\n        <p>Direct communication between nodes eliminates the need for intermediary servers or gateways.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature-card reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.7s\">\n        <h3>Decentralization</h3>\n        <p>Removes the \"Single Point of Failure\" by stripping away the central authority.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature-card reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.9s\">\n        <h3>Consensus Mechanisms</h3>\n        <p>Algorithmic agreements (like PoW or PoS) ensure all nodes agree on the ledger's state.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
      "snapshot_b64": null,
      "approved": true
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "title": "Security Architecture and Immutability",
      "html": "<section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font-body);\">\n  <style>\n    .slide-content {\n      width: 90%;\n      max-width: 1100px;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 3rem;\n    }\n    .slide-title {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem);\n      color: var(--text);\n      text-align: center;\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n    .mechanism-container {\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: space-between;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 1rem;\n      padding: 2rem 0;\n      overflow-x: auto;\n    }\n    .chain-node {\n      flex: 1;\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 2px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      padding: 1.5rem;\n      text-align: center;\n      position: relative;\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;\n    }\n    .chain-node:hover {\n      border-color: var(--accent);\n      transform: translateY(-5px);\n      box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);\n    }\n    .chain-node .node-label {\n      font-size: 0.9rem;\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n      display: block;\n    }\n    .chain-node .hash-val {\n      font-family: monospace;\n      font-size: clamp(0.7rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      word-break: break-all;\n    }\n    .chain-arrow {\n      color: var(--border);\n      font-size: 2rem;\n      font-weight: bold;\n    }\n    .points-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));\n      gap: 1.5rem;\n    }\n    .point-card {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      padding: 1.5rem;\n      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);\n      border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    .point-card h3 {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem);\n      margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;\n      color: var(--accent);\n    }\n    .point-card p {\n      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.2vw, 1rem);\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      margin: 0;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      animation: fadeInUp 0.6s forwards;\n      animation-delay: var(--delay);\n    }\n    @keyframes fadeInUp {\n      to {\n        opacity: 1;\n        transform: translateY(0);\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-content\">\n    <h1 class=\"slide-title reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.1s\">Security Architecture and Immutability</h1>\n\n    <div class=\"mechanism-container\">\n      <div class=\"chain-node reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.3s\">\n        <span class=\"node-label\">Block N</span>\n        <div class=\"hash-val\">Prev: 0000<br>Hash: 8a2f1c</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"chain-arrow reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.4s\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"chain-node reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.5s\">\n        <span class=\"node-label\">Block N+1</span>\n        <div class=\"hash-val\">Prev: 8a2f1c<br>Hash: 3b9e7d</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"chain-arrow reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.6s\">→</div>\n      <div class=\"chain-node reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.7s\">\n        <span class=\"node-label\">Block N+2</span>\n        <div class=\"hash-val\">Prev: 3b9e7d<br>Hash: f4a2c1</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"points-grid\">\n      <div class=\"point-card reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.9s\">\n        <h3>Cryptographic Chaining</h3>\n        <p>Each record contains a hash of the previous block, creating a mathematical link that spans the entire history.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"point-card reveal\" style=\"--delay: 1.1s\">\n        <h3>Immutable Records</h3>\n        <p>Once committed, data cannot be edited or deleted without breaking the chain, rendering the ledger append-only.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"point-card reveal\" style=\"--delay: 1.3s\">\n        <h3>Alteration Prevention</h3>\n        <p>Changing a single bit of data changes the resulting hash, immediately alerting the system to unauthorized tampering.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"point-card reveal\" style=\"--delay: 1.5s\">\n        <h3>Absolute Integrity</h3>\n        <p>Trust is shifted from a central authority to the immutable laws of mathematics and distributed verification.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
      "snapshot_b64": null,
      "approved": true
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "title": "The Convergence: AI and IoT Integration",
      "html": "<section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <style>\n    .slide {\n      background-color: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      font-family: var(--font-body);\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);\n      gap: 2rem;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .slide-header {\n      margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    }\n    .slide-title {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);\n      color: var(--text);\n      margin: 0;\n      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--text), var(--accent));\n      -webkit-background-clip: text;\n      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n    }\n    .grid-container {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n      gap: 2rem;\n      flex-grow: 1;\n    }\n    .concept-card {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 1rem;\n      padding: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);\n      position: relative;\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 1rem;\n    }\n    .concept-card:hover {\n      border-color: var(--accent);\n      transform: translateY(-5px);\n    }\n    .concept-card h3 {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.75rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n    .concept-card p {\n      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem);\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      animation: revealIn 0.6s forwards;\n      animation-delay: var(--delay);\n    }\n    @keyframes revealIn {\n      to {\n        opacity: 1;\n        transform: translateY(0);\n      }\n    }\n    .visual-accent {\n      position: absolute;\n      top: 0;\n      right: 0;\n      width: 40px;\n      height: 40px;\n      background: var(--accent-glow);\n      filter: blur(15px);\n      border-radius: 50%;\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"slide-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"slide-title reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.1s\">The Convergence: AI and IoT Integration</h1>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"grid-container\">\n    <div class=\"concept-card reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.3s\">\n      <div class=\"visual-accent\"></div>\n      <h3>Autonomous Intelligence</h3>\n      <p>AI-driven smart contracts that trigger based on real-world IoT telemetry, enabling self-executing agreements without human intermediaries.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"concept-card reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.5s\">\n      <div class=\"visual-accent\"></div>\n      <h3>Secure Identity & Data</h3>\n      <p>Unique decentralized IDs for every IoT sensor, ensuring secure telemetry and verifiable data provenance for AI training sets.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"concept-card reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.7s\">\n      <div class=\"visual-accent\"></div>\n      <h3>Decentralized Learning</h3>\n      <p>Distributed AI model training where IoT edge devices compute gradients locally, preserving privacy via federated learning.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"concept-card reveal\" style=\"--delay: 0.9s\">\n      <div class=\"visual-accent\"></div>\n      <h3>Machine Economy</h3>\n      <p>M2M micro-payments allowing IoT devices to purchase resources or sell data autonomously using high-throughput blockchain layers.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
      "snapshot_b64": null,
      "approved": true
    }
